# skill: dev-locate
# purpose: Find dependencies and existing patterns (RPOLES Phase 4: LOCATE)
# triggers: Outline created

## Invocation
```
dev-locate <task-id> [--outline <outline-file>] [--verbose]
```

## Output
Creates: `memory/tasks/<task-id>/dependencies.md`

## Implementation Flow

### 1. Load Context
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# dev-locate.skill implementation

TASK_ID="$1"
OUTLINE_FILE="${2:-memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/outline.md}"

if [ ! -f "$OUTLINE_FILE" ]; then
    echo "Error: Outline file not found. Run dev-outline first."
    exit 1
fi

OUTLINE=$(cat "$OUTLINE_FILE")
```

### 2. Locate Dependencies
```bash
# Extract file list from outline
FILES=$(grep "^### File:" "$OUTLINE_FILE" | sed 's/### File: //')

# For each file, find dependencies
for FILE in $FILES; do
    # Find imports/references in existing codebase
    DEPS=$(grep -r "$(basename $FILE)" --include="*.py" --include="*.js" --include="*.ts" . 2>/dev/null | head -20)

    # Find similar patterns
    SIMILAR=$(find . -name "*$(basename $FILE)*" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -10)

    # Find related tests
    TESTS=$(find . -name "*test*$(basename ${FILE%.*})*" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -10)
done
```

### 3. Create Dependency Document
```markdown
# Dependencies: <task-id>

## External Dependencies
### Packages/Libraries
| Package | Version | Purpose | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| <pkg> | <ver> | <what> | <where> |

### Services/APIs
| Service | Endpoint | Authentication | Rate Limit |
|---|---|---|---|
| <service> | <url> | <auth> | <limit> |

## Internal Dependencies

### Affected Files
| File | Relationship | Impact |
|------|---|---|
| <path> | <imports|uses|modifies> | <high/med/low> |

### Related Components
```bash
# Find related components
grep -r "import.*$(component-name)" --include="*.py" --include="*.js" --include="*.ts" . 2>/dev/null | cut -d: -f1 | sort -u
```

