```bash
# Find existing test patterns
find . -path ./node_modules -prune -o -name "*test*.py" -print 2>/dev/null | head -10
```

**Test Style Observed:**
- Test file location: <pattern>
- Test framework: <name>
- Mocking approach: <approach>

